casebody.data:
June 24, 1955.

Decisions Per Curiam:

No. 2963. In the Matter of the Application of Bishop Trust Company, Limited, Trustee, to Register Title to Land Situate at Kalia, Honolulu, Territory of Hawaii. Per Curiam.

The petition for rehearing in the above-entitled cause is denied without argument. Masaji Marumoto for the petition.
